Brown's committee assignments are as follows.<ref>{{cite news |work=[[The Boston Herald]] |url=http://www.bostonherald.com/news/us_politics/view.bg?articleid=1236700&pos=breaking |title=Scott Brown gets key Senate committee assignments |date=March 2, 2010 |accessdate=July 5, 2010}}</ref>
